FBIS4-15583 "drsov069_r_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-069 Daily Report 9 Apr 1994 Azerbaijan New `Boz Gurd' Political Party Registered New `Boz Gurd' Political Party Registered NC0904202094 Baku TURAN in English 1628 GMT 9 Apr 94 NC0904202094 Baku TURAN English BFN [Text] Baku (April 9) TURAN -- Azerbaijan's Ministry of Justice registered a new political party, "Boz Gurd" (Gray Wolf). The Chairman of the Party, Bakhtiyar Akhmedov, said that the name of the party is an ancient Turkish symbol, which shows the unity and integrity of the state. "Our party has nothing in common with nationalist party functioning in Turkey". According to Akhmedov, "Boz Gurd" is an opposition party but does support a political struggle during wartime conditions. "Boz Gurd" calls for new parliamentary elections in the country.
